72
00:04:31,410 --> 00:04:33,390
Apa dia mencari Adipati Chang?

73
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,080
Mungkin saja.

74
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,199
Saat Yan Ming memperbaiki buku,

75
